				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Song upgrades, what upgrades?<a name="13946"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 28 03 11:13 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Is it just me or is the upper end of the game songs not really are upgrades the shield songs get weaker, damage stays same from lvl 60 chants with fufils, ds dont go up, mana regen caps at 20 tick.
<br />

<br />
Looking at all other classes the diff between lvl 60 spells and 64 are HUGE compared to bard song, I hope this changes with new expansion they don't seem to know what high lvl bards need.
<br />

<br />
I think high lvl bards need an AE stun song for upper levels CC, i find it odd that we don't have one, i often do ldon without enchanters and are on pulling/CC.
<br />

<br />
Since our whole sta regen is now gone i think an AE stun song would add to our CC abilities.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"><hr size="1" align="left" width="15%">Phugg lvl 65 Bard on Veeshan</span></td>
