				<td colspan="2"><span>with TDok and IM3
<br />

<br />
Level 60 bard = 114 per tick
<br />
Level 65 bard = 145 per tick
<br />

<br />
That's 28% increase in damage, guaranteed.
<br />

<br />

<br />
As for wizard damage increase....
<br />

<br />
Shock of Magic is a random 1200-3000 hit. More often than not it hits in the 2000-2500 range. It is the worst lvl 65 nuke due to the huge range in damage.
<br />
The most reliable 'big hitter' level 65 nuke is SoS which has a base max of 2740.
<br />

<br />
Compare that to Garrisons which has a base max of 2100.
<br />

<br />
On average, you're looking at a damage increase of roughly 31%.
<br />

<br />

<br />
I guess it's a little more balanced than you think.</span></td>
